fields.name: Iphone 14
fields.description:
The iPhone 14 comes with a 6.1-inch OLED display in Midnight color with 128GB of built-in storage. The Super Retina XDR display has a resolution of 2532x1170 pixels. This model has a six-core A15 Bionic processor. The device uses a nano SIM card.
To access the Internet, you can use a mobile connection of all standards (up to 5G) or Wi-Fi. The smartphone has modules for wireless data transmission NFC and Bluetooth version 5.3. To protect your privacy, you can set an unlock using the face recognition sensor.
This model is equipped with two rear cameras and one front camera. The resolution of each is 12 megapixels. The main modules are equipped with flash, optical and digital zoom and stabilizer. The device allows you to record video in 4K quality (3840x2160 pixels).
The case is made of aluminum, the glass is made using Ceramic Shield technology. The device has an IP72 moisture protection class, thanks to which it will not suffer when immersed to a depth of up to 6 m.
